Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Developer position with DP World. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack development, backend systems, and AI-driven solutions, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

